，在阿姆斯特丹郊區的[[史基浦機場|史基浦機場]]墜毀，機身分成三部分，沒有造成火災。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://avherald.com/h?article=41595ec3&opt=0 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2009-02-25 |archive-date=2018-11-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181106143315/http://avherald.com/h?article=41595ec3&opt=0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>飛機墜毀處離跑道約3[[公里|公里]]，A9公路以北<ref name="CNN article"/><ref name="bbc">{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/europe/7909683.stm |title=Turkey plane crashes in Amsterdam |accessdate=2009-02-25 |archive-date=2019-03-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190330171059/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/europe/7909683.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。9人死亡，55人受傷。

== 降落受損傷 ==


该[[波音737-800|波音737-800]]飞机严重损毁，断成三截，但沒有起火。机上共有127名乘客7名机组人员<ref>[http://www.thy.com/DarkSiteEN/crash_info.aspx Accident Information Page on THY Web Site]</ref><ref name="reuters">{{Cite web |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/newsOne/idUSTRE51O2J020090225 |title=Turkish airliner crashes at Amsterdam airport, 1 dead |accessdate=2009-02-25 |archive-date=2009-03-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090319184232/http://www.reuters.com/article/newsOne/idUSTRE51O2J020090225 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name ="minister1">{{Cite web |url=http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/english/world/11081633.asp?gid=244 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2009-02-25 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924082020/http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/english/world/11081633.asp?gid=244 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 事後 ==
救援人员迅速到达事故地点。大约20辆救护车，以及一些直升机和消防车到达现场。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/worldnews/article-1155022/One-dead-plane-carrying-135-passengers-crashes-breaks-pieces-Amsterdam-airport.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2009-02-25 |archive-date=2012-08-02 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20120802130854/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/worldnews/article-1155022/One-dead-plane-carrying-135-passengers-crashes-breaks-pieces-Amsterdam-airport.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

起初，根据土耳其政府方面的消息和媒体报道，此事故未造成人员死亡，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.agi.it/world/news/200902251240-cro-ren0041-art.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2009-03-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090303145459/http://www.agi.it/world/news/200902251240-cro-ren0041-art.html |archivedate=2009-03-03 }}</ref>不过阿姆斯特丹机场当局否认了该说法。

根据一机场发言人，所有进出史基浦机场的航班被暂时中止。在国际协调时11时15分，有消息称至少Kaagbaan跑道(06/24)已经重新开放。A9公路也被关闭。A4和A13的车道也被关闭，便于紧急服务抵达事故现场。

